These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, february, january
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, fonseca, bongani, baccarat
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the montecristo-smoker##8
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the baccarat-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the baccarat-smoker##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the bongani-smoker##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Birthday   | july | january   | november   | february  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Cigar     | montecristo    | bongani | fonseca     | baccarat    |

