.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, analyst, fisherman, dressmaker
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, green, red, apricot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the fan of salsa is between the owner of the dog and the fan of indie##2
 2. the analyst is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 4. the designer is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who likes apricot is not to the right of the dressmaker##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the dressmaker is on the left of the analyst##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
17. the designer is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who likes green is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Job      | designer | fisherman | dressmaker  | analyst  |
| Color          | apricot     | green | amber | red  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

