There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, almond-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who likes lilac##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person who likes pink##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes lilac is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
12. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Color   | lilac     | pink  | yellow   | emerald      |
