.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
House: futuristic, craftsman, townhouse, tower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, scientific, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the townhouse house is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 2. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching sports movies##2
 5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the tower house is in an odd position##4
 8. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
 9. the tower house is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the townhouse house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
14. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | cucumber    | banana             | apple   | plum     |
| House   | futuristic | townhouse            | tower | craftsman    |
| Movie-Genre     | sports | romance | fantasy  | scientific |
| Sport   | basketball  | golf               | rowing  | tennis   |

