 4. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes pink##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who likes green is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
 7. the person who likes blue is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
 8. the manager is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person who likes blue##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the musician is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the manager is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
13. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
14. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes green##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the manager##8

