 9. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
13. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
14. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
