The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, snooker, go
 1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 4. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 8. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | western   | disaster     | documentary    | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Game     | mah-jongg     | snooker | go | whist     |

