 3. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##8
