 9. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who likes azure##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
