 2. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 6. the person driving the van is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
12. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8

