House: tower, craftsman, modern, wooden
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the wooden house##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the craftsman house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 6. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the wooden house and the person who's birthday is in june##7
11. the modern house is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta        | coffee        | water   |
| Hobby       | card-games      | camping      | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Birthday         | june | december | october     | july  |
| House   | modern          | tower      | craftsman     | wooden  |

