.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, ritmeester, bluemaster, montecristo
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
 4. the person drinking milk is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Beverage           | coffee | iced-tea    | lemonade | milk    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Cigar   | blend   | bluemaster      | ritmeester         | montecristo     |

 